project.name: Home Operations
project.description:
We (@danmanners, @bjw-s, @buroa and I) are looking to centralize a bunch of projects the Home Operations group has been working on for years, some of these included are listed below.

We have had the home-operations github org for awhile now and we finally now have time to work on migrating repos to it. Having a teams account would really help consolidate the passwords, pats, tokens and more that are needed to support such projects
